					"type": 23,
					"value": "Full context from combat - \r\n\r\nwe’d like to request some voicebarks for Captain Therezzyn combat in Creche\n\r\n\r\n\nTherezzyn’s second turn (first one she calls for the guards)\n\nTherezzyn: You die here and by my sword, intruder!\n\n\r\n\r\nTherezzyn’s third turn\n\nTherezzyn: Die already! I won’t be embarrassed in front of my troops again!"
